properties.name: Austrian Ski Resort
properties.description: Posted by Stevedann Ski trip - local band, too much Schnapps. Foregone conclusion that I would get up and jam an REM song or two. The bar owners offered me the season, but I had to go back to work.

properties.description: Posted by StevedannBarcelonaWe tried busking on the streets of Barcelona, but the Spanish didn\'t seem familiar with the concept - the Ramblas had piped music all the way along and one person helpfully suggested I sold my guitar if I needed the money. Probably should\'ve.
